title: Ukraine’s Zelenskyy says thanks to Türkiye’s efforts they achieved ‘serious humanitarian results’
text:
Türkİye, World, Russia-Ukraine War
Ukraine’s Zelenskyy says thanks to Türkiye’s efforts they achieved ‘serious humanitarian results’
Ukraine's president thanks his Turkish counterpart, people for their support for Kyiv’s territorial integrity, sovereignty and independence
ISTANBUL
Ukrainian President Volodymyr Zelenskyy on Friday said that they achieved “serious humanitarian results” thanks to Türkiye’s efforts.
Speaking at a joint press conference with his Turkish counterpart Recep Tayyip Erdogan in Istanbul, Zelenskyy thanked him and the Turkish people for their support for Kyiv’s territorial integrity, sovereignty and independence.
Zelenskyy arrived on an official visit to Türkiye earlier in the day, together with a delegation that also included Ukrainian Defense Minister Rustem Umerov.
